andra Kanu to Compete on 'The Bachelor'|publisher=[[WDEA]]|last=Popper|first=Chris|date=September 17, 2019|accessdate=November 21, 2019}}</ref>\n|23\n|[[Bar Harbor, Maine]]\n|Home Care Coordinator\n|rowspan=\"4\"|Week 4\n|rowspan=\"3\"|13\u201315\n|-\n|Kiarra Norman<ref name=\"auto\">{{cite web|url=https://www.etonline.com/the-bachelor-meet-the-30-women-competing-for-peter-webers-heart-136667|title='Bachelor' Meet The 30 Women Competing for Peter Weber's Heart|date=December 16, 2019|work=[[Entertainment Tonight]]|last=Gawley|first=Paige|accessdate=December 17, 2019}}</ref>\n|23\n|[[Kennesaw, Georgia]]\n|Nanny\n|-\n|Savannah Mullins<ref name=Texas /> \n|27\n|[[Houston|Houston, Texas]]\n|Realtor\n|-\n|Alayah Benavidez<ref>{{cite web|url=https://ladycode.blog/2016/06/28/meet-miss-texas-united-states-2016-alayah-benavidez/|title=Meet Miss Texas United States 2016: Alayah Benavidez|date=June 28, 2016|work=Lady Cody|last=Opie|first=Lisa}}</ref><ref name=Texas>{{cite web|url=https://www.sacurrent.com/ArtSlut/archives/2019/12/17/san-antonio-native-and-miss-texas-alayah-benavidez-to-compete-on-the-upcoming-season-of-the-bachelor|title=San Antonio Native and Miss Texas Alayah Benavidez to Compete on the Upcoming Season of ''The Bachelor''|accessdate=December 17, 2019|author=Merka Nelson, Kelly|work=San Antonio Current|date=December 17, 2019}}</ref>\n|24\n|[[Helotes, Texas]]\n|Orthodontist Assistant\n|16{{efn|name=Alayah|Alayah was originally eliminated in Week 3, but was later brought back in Week 4 and got eliminated at the end of that week.}}\n|-\n|Alexa Caves<ref name=\"Illinois\">{{cite web|url=https://www.chicagotribune.com/entertainment/tv/ct-ent-chicago-women-the-bachelor-tv-season-24-20190918-3p5runclurdorhxhr35dg4wore-story.html|title='The Bachelor': Five Chicago-area women, including a former 'Luvabull' dancer, to compete for Pilot Pete's heart|work=[[Chicago Tribune]]|last=Villagomez|first=Jessica|date=September 18, 2019|accessdate=November 21, 2019}}</ref>\n|27\n|